OL,3,CNew tech used by rugby players to see
OL,4,Chow menstrual cycle impacts concussion
OL,6,FThe (WRU) is using a brand new
OL,7,Ftechnique during the to assess the
OL,8,Fimpact a player's periods can have
OL,9,Fwhen they suffer a concussion.
OL,11,FIt is the first time ever that data on
OL,12,Fhas been viewed side-by-side, with the
OL,13,Fhope it will improve the way players
OL,14,Fare treated.
OL,16,FThe technique, which is being used by
OL,17,Fthe union's strength and conditioning
OL,18,Fteam, has never been used before
OL,19,Foutside of research studies.
