OL,7,Fcaptured more frequently and analysed
OL,8,Ffaster, according to the
OL,10,FPrevious research has suggested
OL,11,Fhormone variation may lead women to
OL,12,Fsuffer a higher rate of concussions,
OL,13,Fas well as having more severe and
OL,14,Fprolonged symptoms than men.
OL,16,FThe said changes in hormone levels
OL,17,Fduring the menstrual cycle play a key
OL,18,Frole.
