OL,6,FShe added: "There's also some evidence
OL,7,Fthat suggests it can disrupt a cycle,
OL,8,Fcause an irregular cycle or miss a
OL,9,Fcycle. I think it's important that we
OL,10,Fas a medical team understand that."
OL,12,FOver the past year, players have been
OL,13,Fusing the application PLAYER.Connect
OL,14,Fto track their wellbeing.
OL,16,FA new feature on the app will also
OL,17,Fallow them to track concussion
OL,18,Fsymptoms.
