OL,6,FJohn Mulcahy, PLAYER.Connect
OL,7,FPerformance Consultant said: "We're
OL,8,Ftracking twenty-four symptoms here, as
OL,9,Fwell as then asking them to give an
OL,10,Foverview on how they feel.
OL,12,F"Think about a players life day to
OL,13,Fday, it's very cognitive, so if
OL,14,Fmentally we can make sure that their
OL,15,Frecovery is tracked, it can make that
OL,16,Fpart easier."
OL,18,FWales Women's Captain, Hannah Jones,
OL,19,Fhas been using the app to log her
OL,20,Fmenstrual cycle.
