OL,6,FShe said: "Once you gather up that
OL,7,Finformation, you understand the
OL,8,Fdifferent phases. In phase two, for
OL,9,Fmyself, I can really push myself in
OL,10,Fthe gym and I feel good. During phase
OL,11,Fthree, I pick up illness and I don't
OL,12,Fsleep very well."
OL,14,FBy logging her symptoms, Hannah says
OL,15,Fthey have now been able to put a plan
OL,16,Fin place which best suits her cycle.
