OL,6,F"During phase three, I increase my
OL,7,Fcarbs, maybe in the gym I'll ease off
OL,8,Fa little bit and make sure rest and
OL,9,Frecovery is key so I don't pick up
OL,10,Fcolds and flus."
OL,12,FHead coach, Ioan Cunningham, said the
OL,13,Finformation gathered every day through
OL,14,Fthis technology has allowed them as a
OL,15,Fteam to adapt players' training plans.
OL,17,FHe said: "The players' health is far
OL,18,Fmore important than a single game, so
OL,19,Fif a player needs an extra week, they
OL,20,Fwill have an extra week."
